Global RoverX,RoverY,ImageID

Rem --- Initialisation ---
RoverX = 100
RoverY = 100
ImageID = 1
Rem Image 1 = gauche, Image 2 = droite
Screen Open 0,320,200,16,Lowres
Curs Off
Flash Off
Cls 2
Hide On

Set Sprite Buffer 256

Rem --- Palette BOB personnalisée ---
Get Sprite Palette 0
Rem Banque Object Editor 0
Colour 0,$FA4
Colour 16,$000
Colour 17,$555
Colour 18,$888
Colour 19,$AAA
Colour 20,$DDD
Colour 21,$000
Colour 22,$000
Colour 23,$000
Colour 24,$000
Colour 25,$000
Colour 26,$000
Colour 27,$000
Colour 28,$000
Colour 29,$000
Colour 30,$000
Colour 31,$000

Rem --- Affiche le sprite hardware 0 ---
Sprite 0,RoverX,RoverY,0,ImageID

While 1
    Wait Vbl

    Rem --- Déplacement ---
    If Key State(79) : RoverX = RoverX - 2 : ImageID = 1
    Else If Key State(78) : RoverX = RoverX + 2 : ImageID = 2
    Else If Key State(77) : RoverY = RoverY - 2
    Else If Key State(76) : RoverY = RoverY + 2
    Else If Key State(69) : End
    End If

    Rem --- Repositionne le sprite ---
    Sprite 0,RoverX,RoverY,0,ImageID

Wend
